
  <sn><md> ### Basic Dressing Setup

A simple and organized wardrobe makes daily life easier. Instead of owning too many clothes, a well-planned basic dressing setup focuses on **comfort at home, professionalism at work, and elegance for special occasions**. Along with clothing, personal care essentials complete a balanced lifestyle.</md></sn>
